data.description: Beautiful home located in Susquehanna Township. It features two large bedrooms with a potential third bedroom and 2.5 baths. It is an end unit so it has a nice size side yard. Property is in great condition and features an attached sunroom/office leading to a private deck. The second floor features a loft area also perfect for an office/computer/study area. Large closets. New roof. New windows. New hot water heater. Washer and dryer.
